6	//! Inline PTX support.
7	//!
8	//! User code should use [`ptx_asm!`](crate::ptx_asm), not the hidden functions
9	//! in this module. The hidden functions are compiler markers: the MIR importer
10	//! recognizes calls to them and replaces those calls with inline PTX.
